<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>글쓰기 - 해골방 갤러리</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: "돋움", sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 2em; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; }
    input, textarea { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0.5em; }
    button { padding: 0.5em 1em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>글쓰기</h1>
  <form action="/write" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
    <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목" required />
    <input type="text" name="author" placeholder="작성자" required />
    <textarea name="content" placeholder="내용" rows="6" required></textarea>
    <label>사진 업로드 (선택)</label>
    <input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*" />
    <button type="submit">글 등록</button>
  </form>

  <p><a href="/">← 글 목록으로</a></p>

</body>
</html>



